TY  - JOUR
TI  - Endogenous Formation of Coalitions
AU  - Hart, Sergiu
AU  - Kurz, Mordecai
AB  - [In order to develop a theory of coalition formation and maintenance, we first establish a valuation criterion for each individual player in a given coalition structure. Various stability concepts based on it are then developed and studied.]
